  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment performed. One factor (Discretization error) carries achievedLevel 2 against a requiredLevel 3, yet the decision record records outcome Accepted on the basis of supplementary expert judgment and historical mesh-convergence data from analogous pump geometries. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-AR-02.",
