      "rationale": "Glycerol-water mixture viscosity and density were measured at test temperature and matched in simulation to within 1.3%. Rotational speed was controlled to ±15 RPM (< 0.5% at 3500 RPM); flow rate was controlled to ±0.05 L/min. All input equivalency requirements are satisfied at the required level."
    }
